comments: Mann (LAC) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Anunoby (TOR) and places two hands on his back as he disengages and the contact is marginal.
Siakam (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Mann (LAC) and places two hands on his back as he disengages and the contact is marginal.
Coffey (LAC) makes marginal contact with Siakam's (TOR) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his shot near the rim.
Kennard (LAC) and Trent Jr. (TOR) briefly engage and disengage.
Trent Jr. (TOR) makes marginal contact with Mann's (LAC) arm after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Morris Sr. (LAC) makes marginal contact with VanVleet's (TOR) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Siakam (TOR) legally contests Morris Sr.'s (LAC) jump shot attempt.
Mann (LAC) commits a take foul on Anunoby (TOR).
Jackson (LAC) extends his leg and creates the marginal contact with Anunoby (TOR).
